node.text:
i’d die for Cappy
-
📹: @cappybears
Original Caption:
“Cappy is an extraordinary kitty. 
This is our typical bed time routine. My favorite part is the purrito. 

**If you're new, Cappy has nerve damage, and as a result of the condition, he is unable to control his bladder. Cappy's bladder can partially empty when he is fully relaxed, but his bladder will never fully empty. I care for Cappy by expressing his bladder every 8-10 hours. I've been doing this for four years.”
